-0.01678858,-0.01606133,-0.05833245,-0.00184149,0.0302071,0.01117997,-0.04954456,0.01968445,-0.00439877,-0.00029126,-0.04085633,-0.01461043,0.01204828,0.01860076,-0.06510257,-0.00687758,0.01963098,-0.02466364,-0.01955313,0.01137293,0.00806647,-0.01985893,0.05206233,-0.03580554,0.01461254,-0.01939415,0.02191452,0.00722644,0.00239574,-0.00874209,0.01102662,0.02496205,-0.0139429,0.06725592,0.02816406,-0.00071294,0.02216337,0.02107839,0.02625711,0.01268639,0.02792305,-0.0036606,-0.01655004,-0.04170646,-0.03949848,0.01103623,0.04198361,0.07097887,0.01794521,-0.02368078,-0.03738412,0.01296958,-0.0010635,-0.00928458,0.011849,-0.04614695,-0.09432981,-0.03641639,0.03244451,0.00067518,0.04593446,0.02918693,0.05632278,0.00853886,0.03821506,0.02067986,0.00819234,0.02975333,0.00473682,0.02186455,0.03822849,0.05622111,0.00133186,-0.04187379,-0.09849937,0.02941262,0.01955456,-0.02914119,-0.03155417,0.00170241,-0.06409217,-0.02873674,0.01899092,-0.02056924,-0.06882116,0.01194885,0.02694215,0.06537373,0.00096548,-0.00692226,-0.01216135,0.03785874,0.00387282,-0.00187857,-0.05125332,-0.01080385,0.02310333,0.05379324,-0.00909783,0.0473568,-0.00174491,-0.02300439,0.07782577,0.03201493,0.00802721,-0.06317846,0.0458234,0.00888291,0.03623015,-0.04343825,0.03438567,0.00000144,0.04177391,-0.01959282,-0.06224569,0.00283634,-0.01055405,0.03543334,-0.00302234,-0.0567407,0.04056637],"last_embed":{"hash":"48bd79b3b08ad3562e231000f27bcda3cb11a9468f42f51323787ce29b21cc0d","tokens":1337}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"48bd79b3b08ad3562e231000f27bcda3cb11a9468f42f51323787ce29b21cc0d","at":1742533451172},"key":"DDD 的实战（第十章）.md#","lines":[1,27],"size":3559,"outlinks":[{"title":"This is especially true in a process that emphasizes refactoring.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":5},{"title":"When software doesn’t have a clean design, developers dread even looking at the existing mess, much less making a change that could aggravate the tangle or break something through an unforeseen dependency.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":8},{"title":"In any but the smallest systems, this fragility places a ceiling on the richness of behavior it is feasible to build. It stops refactoring and iterative refinement.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":11},{"title":"that从句","target":"that从句","line":13},{"title":"从句详解#^83b0df","target":"从句详解#^83b0df","line":14},{"title":"Supple design is the complement to deep modeling.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":17},{"title":"Through the iterative cycle, you hammer that material into a useful shape,cultivating a model that simply and clearly captures the key concerns, and shaping a design that allows a client developer to really put that model to work.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":19},{"title":"To create elements that can be assembled into elaborate systems and still be understandable, a dedication to MODEL-DRIVEN DESIGN has to be joined with a moderately rigorous design style.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":21},{"title":"The same person might well play both roles—even switch back and forth in minutes—but the relationship to the code is different nonetheless.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":23},{"title":"It must follow the contours of a deep model of the domain, so most changes bend the design at flexible points.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":25}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
