5,-0.02048841,-0.02123589,-0.04613647,-0.01278505,0.03293523,0.03162501,0.00099507,0.02511773,0.01521289,0.00878984,-0.03467464,-0.025659,0.00358338,0.05186174,-0.04268068,0.01136917,-0.00888679,0.00345651,-0.00904338,0.07053456,-0.0676699,0.00087325,0.00041077,-0.00639968,0.01043706,-0.02362453,0.03119192,-0.00488333,-0.01552047,-0.01930182,0.0418261,0.05720625,-0.02321233,0.02985641,0.03344256,0.02862583,-0.04905833,0.00929319,0.04503622,-0.01248301,-0.01113308,-0.03308859,0.01008793,-0.06411468,-0.02547362,0.03238399,0.01912423,0.09073905,0.01774037,-0.00816953,-0.06384327,-0.04558681,-0.02124214,-0.01314923,0.01640859,-0.04049362,-0.04756305,-0.01019594,0.01826353,0.00669091,0.01728638,0.04398737,0.01458262,-0.03970345,0.00882106,-0.01343784,-0.06021325,-0.00365069,-0.01031717,0.03885852,0.04649295,0.02174717,0.03626831,-0.03518189,-0.01535394,0.01753971,0.0525306,-0.02822613,-0.03581351,0.04078334,-0.03161381,-0.00232259,-0.00672256,-0.05253013,-0.06562326,0.00328436,0.09166564,0.0614669,-0.00688418,-0.00229368,-0.04743692,0.03550414,-0.00838665,0.03272692,-0.0237468,-0.04034104,0.03782596,0.05506722,-0.05686651,0.01312126,-0.01450115,0.01645777,0.10297225,0.01715106,0.01390375,-0.07997851,0.044973,0.02891743,-0.01050776,-0.02334073,-0.02001321,0.00000125,0.00054872,0.00717242,-0.05155579,-0.01407871,0.01865014,-0.00573004,0.01184906,-0.05961347,0.01132581],"last_embed":{"hash":"426f5427f66fb40249a6c79fa96ec43333669934ebd67ddaef4300e6e0427e5e","tokens":1002}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"426f5427f66fb40249a6c79fa96ec43333669934ebd67ddaef4300e6e0427e5e","at":1742533454404},"key":"DDD 的实战（第十章）.md#Standalone Classes#{1}","lines":[134,150],"size":2718,"outlinks":[{"title":"And interdependencies pile up easily.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":1},{"title":"But even a MODULE can be a lot to think about withoutan almost fanatical commitment to controlling dependencies within it.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":3},{"title":"In every programming environment, a few basics are so pervasive that they are always in mind.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":5},{"title":"Practically speaking, “integers” don’t add to the intellectual load.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":8},{"title":"Implicit concepts, recognized or unrecognized, count just as much as explicit references. Although we can generally ignore dependencies on primitive values such as integers and strings, we can’t ignore what theyrepresent.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":10},{"title":"This scrutiny starts with the factoring of the model concepts themselves. Then it requires attention to each individual association and operation. Model and design choices can chip away at dependencies—often to zero.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":13},{"title":"Every such self-contained class significantly eases the burden of understanding a MODULE.","target":"obsidian://booknote?type=annotation&book=resources/Domain-Driven%20Design%20Tackling%20Complexity%20in%20the%20Heart%20of%20Software%20by%20Eric%20Evans%20(z-lib.org","line":15}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
